      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Obytkujeme combined marketing pages with functional booking flows, making it a good example of product-oriented frontend work rather than a simple static site.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "The application included landing pages, image-heavy presentation, booking calendar flows, and supporting administrative functionality.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "It also reflects my interest in frontend delivery that balances user experience, maintainability, and practical production concerns such as deployment and incremental updates.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
